room_title: Escape room "Operation Night Light" by Escape Cedar Valley in Cedar Falls
room_address: 115 E 4th Street, Suite 101 Cedar Falls, IA 50613
room_description: It seems a greedy scientist has developed a weapon to disable the North American power grid and it’s up to you and your team of agents to break into his remote cabin to secure the hard drive before it’s too late.  Do you have what it takes to save America or will it be lights out?
